title: Gym, Sundeck, Grills, Lounge, Package Room, CTA,+ close to everything!
posting_body: ['The Van der Rohe Apartments in Lakeview East are conveniently located near grocery stores, shopping, dining and the lakefront.', 'This north-facing unit is spacious, has hardwood heated flooring, and is located within a few minutes walk to Lincoln Park, the Lakefront Trail and Diversey Driving Range!', 'This unit (#2933-504) is $1,820 per month.', 'About the Apartment:', '- Floor to ceiling windows', '- Granite Countertops', '- Hardwood Flooring', '- Air Conditioning', '- Marble Bathrooms', '- SS Appliances', '- Dishwasher', '- Microwave', '- Window Coverings', 'About the Community:', '- 24/7 Fitness Center', '- Large Sundeck', '- Grilling Stations', '- Resident Lounge', '- Attached Parking', '- Bike Room', '- Package Room', 'Walk to:', '- Lakefront Trail', '- Lake Michigan', '- Lincoln Park', '- Diversey Driving Range', "- Trader Joe's, Mariano's, Go Grocer", '- Shopping + Dining', 'Visit our website at <URL> to view live availability and for more information!', 'Disclaimer: Pricing, availability, lease terms and specials are subject to change.', 'Apartment availability and lease terms may vary.', 'Please note that the price may be net effective of a special and/or concessions that are currently running.', 'Information is believed to be accurate, however, is subject to errors and omissions.', 'Group Fox Management | EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY']
